name: Food Delivery App UI Screens - HB (The Dish App)
description:
"HB - The Dish App" is a Food Delivery UI Kit consisting of 70+ pixel-perfect designed in Figma with lots of love from auto-layout.


The kit is easy to customize, it includes global colour and font styles. It has an easy setup and many features that are required in restaurants. We have designed a full solution for a food delivery app.
